320.title: Victoria: Part 1
320.plot: The owner of Victoria, Aatmaram gets arrested in the murder of Mr. Furniturewala, the owner of an antique shop. K.D. Pathak firmly decides to fight Aatmaram's case and tries to prove him innocent. Nishit Aggrawal, a worker in Mr. Furniturewala's antique shop reveals a shocking truth in the court. Is Aatmaram the murderer? Who is the actual murderer? What is the connection between Victoria, Aatmaram and Mr. Furniturewala?

321.title: Victoria: Part 2
321.plot: One of prime witnesses of Victoria owner Aatmaram's case, Chandan is declared dead in the Hospital. Shravan and Varun are trying to collect more information about the lamp. Nishit reveals a shocking truth about the argument that took place between Firdos and Kailash. Will K.D. Pathak succeed in proving Aatmaram innocent?
